description:
Zen Chess Collection.

A collection of four minimalist chess puzzle games to test your skills in a series of 600 challenges, designed for experienced chess players and newcomers alike.

* Enjoy beautifully designed chess boards and pieces, build with a lot of love and craftsmanship;
* Original soundtrack, specially composed to increase your focus and concentration;
* Four games with 600 puzzles carefully curated by a Chess Grandmaster;

Become a Chessmaster!
